        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAll - \n\nI've introduced a script to do some automated fixes and quality checks.  Please see the commit message for more details.  I've also performed a one-time cleanup of various items that were detected.\n\nOnce merged, please start using this before your commits to ensure standard practices are followed.  If you additional checks or fixes you'd like to see automated, then just let me know.\n\nThanks,\nTrevor",
